title: Merry Xmas Strat
author: shatteredcon
pages:
#- Hi stratmatt57!

I hope you have a pleasant Christmas and holiday season!

I threw in some extra things that I had lying around my chests. I don't have any use for potions but maybe you do?

#- Observation is really the only book I own that might be of interest. Fox used to be a member of Carbon before I joined.

Enjoy the eggs! I traveled all over the map to find them only to have my fellow Carbonites give them to me. At least I got 
#- to see some cities I never have before! I don't leave Carbon much so this was fun searching for eggs for you!

You're always welcome in Carbon!

-shatteredcon, Carbon Magistrate
#- 